  "items": [
    {
      "kind": "title",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ฉันเป็นใคร และเธอเป็นใคร – เรียนรู้การพูดเกี่ยวกับคน",
      "file": "th-th-b44cccd15a33955004aae3650e66b6e7b89ce8b3.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "บทนำ",
      "file": "th-th-861e85f4c23d7d531e15db3e028210fd28a78bbf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ในบทเรียนนี้ เราจะเรียนรู้การพูดว่าเราเป็นใคร และพูดเกี่ยวกับคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-0e4818b09f584d18f6a1c8f8263ff983475af649.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เราจะใช้ประโยคง่าย ๆ เพื่อบอกชื่อและความรู้สึกของคน",
      "file": "th-th-6adfb8a161e0b5cd32142438254ac9716c954317.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "และเราจะจำสิ่งสำคัญอย่างหนึ่ง: พระเจ้ารู้จักทุกคนตามชื่อ",
      "file": "th-th-899580f0a2d709bfe2c17996692ed3ec9ad92843.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "1. พูดเกี่ยวกับตัวเอง",
      "file": "th-th-4a74d5f16d4d4b4350c8ca8f36df9fd3a994b9f5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เมื่อเราพูดเกี่ยวกับตัวเอง เราใช้รูปแบบพิเศษ",
      "file": "th-th-05f3d3cc127651eb78d82cb14b091cf3aea2d33a.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "รูปแบบนี้ช่วยให้เราบอกชื่อหรือความรู้สึกได้",
      "file": "th-th-72dadd8e4967380f33b54a221a44b52d28d1d2e5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2ea7a194959761fc6819b0a71918a66db527430d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am happy.",
      "file": "en-us-23939b7341e0b2db15f437958c508b0842216b70.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "I am Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-5fd7218dba7b66e228565abe8c016114d4e7ab2c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตรงนี้ คนกำลังพูดถึงตัวเอง",
      "file": "th-th-8ff071a1936c989f36f18ea1e6ec9a8fc5681b72.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับพูดว่า: ฉัน",
      "file": "th-th-e7205cbf32adff2257388872f2165319745dbe9b.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "2. พูดกับคนอื่น",
      "file": "th-th-6cf4e6142ee4cd1f33d1717ae70a852909978702.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เมื่อเราพูดกับใครโดยตรง เราใช้รูปแบบอีกแบบหนึ่ง",
      "file": "th-th-e7d46eae3c5e9017a4676b3b5096a42ca237f7d4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ใช้เมื่อเรามองหน้าแล้วพูดกับเขา",
      "file": "th-th-4e122a41a0ac583083be3268330fa64462b38f87.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-d77d87e8e23a7d0f9fa4de519606bdb500208fe4.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-4057e5dd51af2766d75664e2de122f5da27990c9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d88c326c1e116ceabac6175587976a0f555d96a0.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "You are special.",
      "file": "en-us-bd168e4be2ccb03a768f5e99a6affc68421f8f80.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตรงนี้ เรากำลังพูดกับใครบางคน",
      "file": "th-th-cc1c7ea1a50ad7af0bbbef03d92e29d76b2a7097.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับพูดว่า: เธอ",
      "file": "th-th-b4403b7ef235a19b990e8403cde1c89204a9a209.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "3. พูดเกี่ยวกับเด็กผู้ชายหรือผู้ชาย",
      "file": "th-th-1d706aae710c066255ce418350b37d135e68587e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ลองนึกว่าเราพูดถึงเด็กผู้ชายที่ไม่ได้อยู่ในบทสนทนา",
      "file": "th-th-addd4ac18368b3cd7125e728ebd90b9a8e33f749.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เขาไม่ได้พูด และเราไม่ได้พูดกับเขาโดยตรง",
      "file": "th-th-b2780ce55d0f87b0fd8bb1816d4f21127556805e.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรากำลังพูดถึงเขาให้คนอื่นฟัง",
      "file": "th-th-5f41374f91814f7318e0f4dca6fec1255daafcd9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is a boy.",
      "file": "en-us-2a2632a545de1823da43afd6efaf7a9bdde88adf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-82d5659b428ca8187f1b62cd7b1c594773f693e2.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "He is Moses.",
      "file": "en-us-1875dbfb2e551e944cb3613e86530d6cc03308b8.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตรงนี้ เราพูดถึงเด็กผู้ชายหรือผู้ชาย",
      "file": "th-th-87ba6db825dfc38212c489ed4278e83f4b9827e9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับชี้ไปที่เขาแล้วเล่าให้คนอื่นฟัง",
      "file": "th-th-52c4e3af1607b6ca679761ee9a31d604f172ecf0.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "4. พูดเกี่ยวกับเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิง",
      "file": "th-th-813dc28c78157230ff90eb510c90642f18dcfef6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรายังพูดถึงเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิงได้",
      "file": "th-th-c3c5a883fc8f58949299814e5d66ada27aaab7d5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนเดิม เธอไม่ได้พูด และเราไม่ได้พูดกับเธอโดยตรง",
      "file": "th-th-490ae696b6b02bc68a214bf97402171a9811b75c.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เรากำลังพูดถึงเธอ",
      "file": "th-th-c226c19fd01010ba4722180985c724591a413a71.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ดูตัวอย่าง:",
      "file": "th-th-b1943d71cd724b7e30f4be9f47b4b9c9006d52a6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is a girl.",
      "file": "en-us-30ddae33c2bccaca73a4be47e7712fd4c9bfcf94.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
      "lang": "en-US",
      "voice": "en-US-Standard-I",
      "text": "She is happy.",
      "file": "en-us-d1b3d3c880ee376906cd771d820b9756e0aed280.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text-bold-large",
