      "text": "She is Hannah.",
      "file": "en-us-d1fcfedd52306f6c11995ac3e30ad2bbc7bf56f6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "ตรงนี้ เราพูดถึงเด็กผู้หญิงหรือผู้หญิง",
      "file": "th-th-26720bc5b6b09db184cabc89b5e610db66268f5d.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "เหมือนกับชี้ไปที่เธอแล้วเล่าให้ฟัง",
      "file": "th-th-620af4252ba2a6305a6093e524cf5313926106ff.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "subtitle",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
      "text": "5. พระเจ้ารู้จักคุณ",
      "file": "th-th-3701743463ab796a62dad039c82c1c9fc9453d73.mp3"
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "lang": "th-TH",
      "voice": "th-TH-Standard-A",
